any other created being=\r\ns, and interact based on the rules of this dream world. Inside the dream wo=\r\nrld, for the duration of it&#39;s existence, everything appears true.&nbsp;&lt;/di=\r\nv&gt;\n\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The world that is created is based on the thoughts =\r\nthat went through our mind at the moment we fell into deep sleep. At some p=\r\noint, once we have experienced enough, we naturally wake up. We spend some =\r\ntime in the &quot;real world&quot;, and then the cycle repeats.&lt;/div&gt;\n\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div=\r\n&gt;&lt;div&gt;Our experiences inside our created dream world have an impact on us w=\r\nhen we wake up. From time to time, we remember our dreams and reflect on th=\r\nem. The experiences certainly carry on into our waking state to some extent=\r\n, and then back into the next dream experience.&lt;/div&gt;\n\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;=\r\nBy looking at every question from three points of time, we get three differ=\r\nent answers.&nbsp;The dream world is real for it&#39;s duration, unreal between=\r\n cycles and is conditionally real when looking across cycles. Freedom is in=\r\nteracting with the world with no attachment from inside the world; realizin=\r\ng the absolute unreality of the world from outside; and is both of these wh=\r\nen looking across cycles.&lt;/div&gt;\n\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;From all points of vie=\r\nw, the thinning of the accumulated conditioning (vAsanA-tAnavam) is the key=\r\n.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;sasneham,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;=\r\n &nbsp;ajit&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n\n\n&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div clas=\r\ns=3D&quot;yiv776828023gmail_quote&quot;&gt;On Mon, Jul 30, 2012 at 12:04 PM, rajarshi na=\r\nndy &lt;span dir=3D&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;&lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; ymailto=3D&quot;mailto:r